data.description: Looking for a 5 bedroom 3 bath custom home with many updates in Emerald Mountain? This is it!! Large eat-in kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, and a gas cook top. To the left of the kitchen, you have a gathering room with a vaulted ceiling. To the right of the kitchen, you have the family room with a gas fireplace. New closet organizers have been installed in the his/her closets in the master bath. A spacious main floor bedroom with access to a full bathroom is opposite the master. Upstairs you have the 3 bedrooms a full bath plus a bonus room. There are new surround speakers inside and out. Many updates include new ceiling fans, light fixtures, faucets, built-in garage storage, and main floor blinds, as well new paint and grout. Call now for your private showing!
